### shortcuts ###

Mod4 Return :Exec kitty
Mod4 D :Exec rofi -show drun
Mod4 X :Exec dmenu-fb.sh
Mod4 F1 :Exec nautilus
Mod4 F2 :Exec google-chrome
Mod4 F3 :Exec kitty -e ncmpcpp
Mod4 Print :Exec screenshot.sh full
Mod4 Escape :Exec betterlockscreen -l pixel
Mod4 Delete :Exit
Mod4 Shift r :Restart
XF86AudioRaiseVolume :Exec pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ +5%
XF86AudioLowerVolume :Exec pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ -5%
XF86AudioMute :Exec pactl set-sink-mute @DEFAULT_SINK@ toggle

### mousebindings ###

OnDesktop Mouse1 :HideMenus
OnDesktop Mouse3 :RootMenu
OnWindow Mod4 Mouse1 :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {StartMoving}
OnWindow Mod4 Mouse3 :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {StartResizing NearestCorner}
OnWindowBorder Move1 :StartMoving
OnLeftGrip Move1 :StartResizing bottomleft
OnRightGrip Move1 :StartResizing bottomright
OnTitlebar Control Mouse1 :StartTabbing
OnTitlebar Double Mouse1 :Maximize
OnTitlebar Mouse1 :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {ActivateTab}
OnTitlebar Move1 :StartMoving
OnTitlebar Mouse3 :WindowMenu
OnTitlebar Mouse4 :ShadeOn
OnTitlebar Mouse5 :ShadeOff

### keybindings ###

# menu
Mod4 space :RootMenu

# workspaces
Mod4 1 :Workspace 1
Mod4 2 :Workspace 2
Mod4 3 :Workspace 3
Mod4 4 :Workspace 4
Mod4 Shift 1 :TakeToWorkspace 1
Mod4 Shift 2 :TakeToWorkspace 2
Mod4 Shift 3 :TakeToWorkspace 3
Mod4 Shift 4 :TakeToWorkspace 4
Mod1 Control Left :PrevWorkspace
Mod1 Control Right :NextWorkspace

# windows
# focus
Mod1 Tab :NextWindow {groups} (workspace=[current])
Mod1 Shift Tab :PrevWindow {groups} (workspace=[current])
# move
Mod4 Shift Left :MoveTo 0 * Left
Mod4 Shift Right :MoveTo 0 * Right
Mod4 Shift Up :MoveTo * 0 Upper
Mod4 Shift Down :MoveTo * 0 Lower
Mod4 C :MoveTo 0 0 Center
# state
Mod4 Q :Close
Mod4 Z :Minimize
Mod4 M :Maximize
Mod4 T :ToggleDecor
Mod4 U :Shade
Mod4 F :Fullscreen

